OL,4,CChina schools: 'Xi Jinping Thought'
OL,5,Cintroduced into curriculum
OL,6, China will introduce the political
OL,7, ideology of the Chinese President in
OL,8, its national curriculum.
OL,10,F"Xi Jinping thought" will help
OL,11,F"teenagers establish Marxist beliefs",
OL,12,Fsaid the Ministry of Education (MOE) in
OL,13,Fnew guidelines.
OL,15,FThe ideology will be integrated from
OL,16,Fprimary school up to university.
OL,18,FThis is the latest effort by Mr Xi to
OL,19,Fconsolidate the ruling Chinese
OL,20,FCommunist Party's role in different
OL,21,Fareas of society.
